com.klarna.rest.http_transport

Interface HttpTransport

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    HttpUrlConnectionTransport

    public interface HttpTransport
    General interface for an HTTP transport.
    See Also:
    Default HTTP transport based on HttpURLConnection.

        Parameters:
        path - URL path.
        headers - HTTP request headers
        Returns:
        Processed response
        Throws:
        ApiException - if API server returned non-20x HTTP CODE, Content-Type mismatched or response contains a Error
        IOException - if an error occurred when connecting to the server or when parsing a response.
